N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5100.7 - Applicability of regulations to non-corporate entities

State Regulations

For purposes of these regulations, non-corporate entities
shall, to the extent possible, comply with all relevant requirements applicable
to corporate entities. Notes
